<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id748bc10e-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s90108"><num value="90108">§ 90108.</num><heading> Annual audit</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The foundation shall enter into a contract with an independent auditor to conduct an annual audit of the foundation.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id748bc10f-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/107/252/tVI/s601/a">Pub. L. 107–252, title VI, § 601(a)</ref>, <date date="2002-10-29">Oct. 29, 2002</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/116/1721">116 Stat. 1721</ref>, § 152608; renumbered § 90108, <ref href="/us/pl/113/237/s3/c/6/B">Pub. L. 113–237, § 3(c)(6)(B)</ref>, <date date="2014-12-18">Dec. 18, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/2840">128 Stat. 2840</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
